# Build-context filter for the Action Container images (built with this
# directory as context: see docker-compose.yml `actions-server`/`actions-console`).
#
# This directory holds the whole workspace, but the Actions build only needs
# TrajectoryActions + TrajectoryEditor. Ignore everything, then re-include just
# those two, then drop their heavy/irrelevant contents.
#
# (Editor, Runtime and Tester images build from their OWN subdirectory contexts
# and use their own .dockerignore files — this file does not affect them.)

# Ignore everything by default...
*

# ...re-include only the two repos the Action Container build needs.
!TrajectoryActions
!TrajectoryEditor

# Drop heavy / irrelevant content inside the re-included repos.
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.git
**/.claude
**/.planning
**/.superpowers
**/coverage
**/.vs
**/*.log
**/*.db
**/*.db-wal
**/*.db-shm
TrajectoryEditor/electron-dist
TrajectoryEditor/Trajectory-dist
TrajectoryEditor/Trajectory-dist.zip
TrajectoryEditor/.dev-backups
TrajectoryEditor/test-data
TrajectoryEditor/e2e
